data.description: Love the outdoors? Then this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom open floor plan home is perfect for you. Nestled in a picturesque, wooded lot, this large home boasts a family room with woodburning fireplace, sizeable kitchen, spacious living room, first floor laundry, and detached oversized 2 car garage. The back yard features a great deck to enjoy views of the woods and stream on the property. Conveniently located with quick access to I-71 and an easy commute to downtown Columbus. Buckeye Valley Schools. Schedule a showing today!
